dataList.content: Ohh…? Come, friends, and lend your gazes hither!
... What is all of this?
Cars are stacked atop one another as if to form a tower.
Sombre.
What had looked like towering structures from afar were, up close, cars piled into heaps.
Why are there so many cars piled up here?
Oho, some bear scripts upon their wind-shields! These must have been missives from their families!
This one says… “I miss you.” The owners… should be coming back soon for them, right…?
Not a chance.
Even if they did return from the casino, they wouldn’t be in any shape for a happy reunion with their loving families~

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: Well… if I may play the auxiliary role of an impromptu guide... this here is the hidden landmark of these parts of the Backstreets.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: The final stop for gamblers, so to speak.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: And also the stepping stone that helped the Tingtang Gang amass its wealth—dealing in used cars taken from those who had nothing left to offer as the stakes.
So Rodya, you’ve been around places like this pretty often, right? Got anything to add? Bet you could tell us some interesting tidbits.
Nah~ No idea. Don’t remember a thing. I chose to forget the past and live for the future.
... And I'd stick to that promise I made to myself if it weren't for pests bent on getting in my way. Hmph.

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: Oi, bohnen! Who do ya think you are, messin' about on our turf?

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: Or what, ya here to sell ya car or something?
Nay! We mount an omnibus!

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: We're not the ones who specialize dealing in organs, though... Hmm, well, I guess a pair of eyes with colors like yours might fetch a decent price.
So we have come to the right place! We are here for thy leader!

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: Ya got some nerve, marchin’ up to a gang like this. Who do ya work for?
We serve under Limb—!
Ahem...
An awkward silence followed.

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: I asked you a question! Don’t just trail off!
